title: Paris court to rule on Nicolas Sarkozy corruption charge
summary: Former President Nicolas Sarkozy and several associates are accused of accepting millions of euros in illegal campaign funding from Libya's Muammar Gaddafi during Sarkozy's 2007 presidential election. Investigations have revealed alleged financial support from the Libyan regime, raising significant concerns about election integrity. Sarkozy has denied the allegations, calling them unfounded.
